    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the onion is softening, chop the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> into quarters</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 250ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [450ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and add the<strong> tomato paste</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
