    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>ground paprika</strong>, <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> chopped ginger</strong> (save the rest for later!) and most of the<strong> curry powder</strong> (reserve 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2] </span>tsp for the fish!) and cook for 1-2 min</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>tomato stock </strong>and cook for 10-12 min or until the sauce has thickened and the tomatoes have broken down</p>",
